show.description: Framed for his own mother’s murder, Lord King Adithya has spent 2 years in prison for a crime he didn’t commit. Now he embarks on a relentless quest to uncover the true killers—those who took his mother’s life for the stealing jade stone. As he unravels the conspiracy, dark secrets and powerful enemies stand in his way.
